tweet: All Marylanders 18 years and older are now eligible for a COVID-19 booster!  What's the timing? Six or more months after a 2nd dose of Pfizer or Moderna or 2+ months after a Johnson & Johnson single dose. Find appointments at:  https://t.co/WKOMRWvB54 or  https://t.co/Kpu8oYothe  https://t.co/zL2AmnYGTu
